HEADWORD: Ill-omened
<hw>Ill`-o"mened</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Having unlucky
omens; inauspicious. See Note under <er>Ill</er>,
<pos>adv.</pos></def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> ill-fated, ill-starred, unlucky.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

